
'''The Gods must be Crazy''' ni film yo gusetsa yo mu 1980 yanditswe, yakozwe, itunganywa kandi iyobowe na Jamie Uys<ref>FILM VIEW; IS 'THE GODS MUST BE CRAZY' ONLY A ... <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 1984/10/28 › arts › film-view...</ref> . ubufatanyabikorwa mpuzamahanga muri Afrika yepfo na Botswana, ni film yambere muri '''The Gods must be Crazy''' series <ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy movie review (1981) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › the-gods-must-...</ref>.

Iyi filime yashyizwe muri Afurika y'Epfo, ikinamo umuhinzi wo muri Namibiya San Nǃxau ǂToma nka Xi<ref name=":0">'THE GODS MUST BE CRAZY' - A TRULY INTERNATIONAL HIT <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 1985/04/28 › movies › the-go...</ref>, umuhigi-uhiga mu butayu bwa Kalahari umuryango we wavumbuye icupa ry'ikirahure ryamanutse mu ndege, kandi bizera ko ari impano yatanzwe n'imana zabo<ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy | film by Uys | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › topic › The-Gods-Must-B...</ref>. Igihe Xi yiyemeje gusubiza icupa ku mana, urugendo rwe ruba ruhujwe n’umuhanga mu binyabuzima (wakinnye nka Marius Weyers )<ref>African comedy “The Gods Must Be Crazy” to screen at ... <nowiki>https://www.egypttoday.com</nowiki> › Article › African-comed...</ref>, umwarimu w’ishuri ry’umudugudu mushya ( Sandra Prinsloo ), hamwe n’itsinda ry’iterabwoba<ref>The gods must be crazy | The New Times | Rwanda <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › section › read</ref> .

'''''The Gods must be Crazy'''''  yarekuwe na Ster-Kinekor muri Afrika yepfo, aho yakoze amateka yinjiza amafaranga menshi<ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy 1 & 2 (English & Foreign ... - Loot <nowiki>https://www.loot.co.za</nowiki> › product › xdvd-597-g120</ref>, ikaba yarasohoye amafaranga menshi mumateka yinganda za firime za Afrika yepfo<ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › the-gods-must-be-cra...</ref>.  Iyi filime yagenze neza mu bucuruzi no mu bindi bihugu, harimo na Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika<ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy (1980) - Where to Watch It Streaming ... <nowiki>https://reelgood.com</nowiki> › movie › the-gods-must-be-crazy-1...</ref>, aho yatanzwe na 20 Century Fox, aho ibiganiro [[Ikinyafurikansi|by’umwimerere bya Afrikaans]] yashyizwe mu cyongereza<ref>N!xau wamenyekanye ku izina rya Sagatwa ni muntu ki? | IGIHE <nowiki>https://www.igihe.com</nowiki> › abantu › biographies › n-xau-...</ref>. Nubwo byagenze neza, iyi filime yakunze kunengwa kwerekana ubwoko kandi bigaragara ko atazi ivangura  muri Afurika yepfo<ref>Ibitangaje wamenya kuri Nǃxau ǂToma 'Sagatwa' wishwe n ... <nowiki>https://ukwezi.rw</nowiki> › Imyidagaduro › article › Ibitangaje-w...</ref>. 

Film yakurikiwe ni ikindi gice  '''The Gods must be Crazy''' part II  yashyizwe ahagaragara Columbia Pictures mu 1989.

=== Gufata amashusho ===
''The Gods Must Be Crazy yafatiwe amashusho'' i Tsumkwe, muri Namibiya,  ndetse no muri Botswana. <ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy Coke bottle turns 100 - Sunday ... <nowiki>https://www.sundaystandard.info</nowiki> › the-gods-must-be-cr...</ref>Nk’uko Uys abitangaza ngo N! Xau yasubizwaga mu rugo rwe mu butayu bwa Kalahari buri byumweru bitatu cyangwa bine kugira ngo atababazwa n’umuco<ref>The Gods Must Be Crazy - Time Out <nowiki>https://www.timeout.com</nowiki> › movies › the-gods-must-be-...</ref> .  Mu gihe mu mijyi, N! Xau yize kunywa inzoga n'itabi. <ref>Kenya: E-Confessions On M-Church, the Gods Must Be Crazy <nowiki>https://allafrica.com</nowiki> › stories</ref> Uys yavuze ko yishyuye N! Xau $ 300 mu minsi 10 ya mbere yakoraga, ariko ko amafaranga bivugwa ko yatwawe n'umuyaga<ref>Meet the Namibian actor who helped gross $60m for the 1980 ... <nowiki>https://face2faceafrica.com</nowiki> › article › meet-the-namibia...</ref>.  N! Xau yahise yishyurwa n'inka 12. <ref>N!xau, Bushman Who Starred In 'The Gods Must Be Crazy' <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 2003/07/08 › arts › n-xau-bus...</ref> Mu 1985, Uys yavuze ko yohereje N! Xau $ 100 buri kwezi kuva yafata amashusho, N! Xau yakoresheje mu iduka ry’ubucuruzi ku bilometero 60 uvuye aho yahigaga<ref>The Gods Must be Crazy - Mimosa Film Group (mimosafilms.co.za)</ref>; Uys yavuze kandi ko hashyizweho konti y’amadolari 20.000 y’izina rya N! Xau.<ref>The Gods must be Crazy but the Producers Know Exactly what ... <nowiki>https://tspace.library.utoronto.ca</nowiki> › ... › Lee, Richard B.</ref>   

== Controversies ==
''The Gods Must Be Crazy'' yakunze kunengwa kubera ko bigaragara ko ikomeje imyumvire ishingiye ku moko n'ivangura n'ivangura muri Afurika y'Epfo<ref>World History Connected | Vol. 10 No. 1 | Zackry T. Farmer: Revisiting the Gods Must Be Crazy: Revealing the complexity of apartheid South Africa with a comedy classic (uillinois.edu)</ref>.  Muri Amerika, ngo iyi filime yatowe n’inama y’igihugu y’abavoka b’abirabura n’indi mitwe irwanya ivanguramoko ubwo yerekanaga mu nzu ya Street Street ya 68 mu mujyi wa New York. <ref name=":0" />
